```# Flask Tip Calculator App

This Flask app calculates the amount each person should pay after splitting a bill, including a tip, among a specified number of people.

## Installation

To run this app, you need to have Flask installed. You can install it via pip:


### pip install Flask


## Run the App

### python app.py

Access the app in your web browser at http://127.0.0.1:5000. Fill out the form with the total bill amount,
tip percentage, and the number of people splitting the bill.

Click the "Calculate" button to see the amount each person should pay.

```bash
